{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Crosswave\n\n<size=45>A Leader's Prowess<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Exercise Area","dir":1,"bgm":"cw-story","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"They got meeeee!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":301160},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Another dead end... Yukikaze, fall back to our line of defense! Taihou and I will cover you!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You certainly know how to work someone hard... Yukikaze, now!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":307070},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Understood! ... I mean, consider yourselves off the hook for now!","actor":301160,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Somehow, we managed to fend off the Commander's onslaught... But as the battle gets drawn out, we'll surely get whittled down...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Grrr... How is it possible that not even Yukikaze the Great could put a halt to the Commander's fleet...","actor":301160,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It seems we're at a loss. We can adjust our strategy all we want, but Commander's fleet seems to always be a step ahead of us.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":307070},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"There are Eagle Union ships that have managed it before, you know...","actor":301160,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"And, while I wouldn't mind suffering a crushing defeat at my Commander's hands, that would reflect poorly on the Sakura Empire's reputation...","actor":307070,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":4,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I'll admit, one's motivation starts to diminish when a battle feels as one-sided as this... Having said that, we must not resort to using cheap tricks, like Yukikaze said...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"......","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"They're forcing my hand...!","actor":900200,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Taihou, Yukikaze, please listen. I have an idea for how we can turn this around.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"But how? And let me just get this out of the way; I might be lucky, but even I can't magically triple our fleet power!","actor":301160,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"There's still a way for us to get the upper hand in this situation?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":307070},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Yes. By ignoring all the other opponents and going straight for the Commander.","actor":900200,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"No way! Not even Yukikaze the Great could plow through to the center of that massive fleet...","actor":301160,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You won't be alone. We'll bait the ship the Commander is on to come here, then attack all at once.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It doesn't matter if you use cannons or bombs, just take out that flagship! Got it?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"But how do you know where the Commander is?","actor":307070,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Why, I thought you of all people would know, Taihou... Would you mind doing some recon for us?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"expression":5,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Me?! ... Need I even answer that question? I would absolutely love to locate the Commander!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":307070},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Appreciate it. I'll give you specific instructions later, so for now just try not to let the Commander catch wind of our plan.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":900200},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Set sail!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900200,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"JUNHEBOSS3","fadeOut":1.5}